{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531040/extras/GIF_03.gif?t=1718390100\" /><br>Rune Golf is an immersive and contemplative golf game where you play as a solitary golf ball traversing the ruins of a forgotten civilization. Your exploration of these lost ruins will require precision, curiosity, and determination to reach the end of numerous levels! In Rune Golf, you can explore the levels as much as you like, but access to the final hole will close if you exceed the allowed number of shots for each level!<br><br><strong>ADJUST </strong>the power and angle of your shots and navigate through the levels to reach the final hole without exceeding your allowed number of shots!<br><br><strong>MODIFY </strong>your trajectory at any time: a slow-motion mode activates, allowing you to make extraordinary shots!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531040/extras/GIF_02b.gif?t=1718390100\" /><br><strong>TAKE YOUR TIME and EXPLORE</strong> the levels without counting your shots, to identify and optimize your path, and discover hidden secrets and rewards!<br><br><strong>INTERACT and DIALOGUE </strong>with the small spirits that inhabit these ruins to uncover the secrets of this lost civilization.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531040/extras/GIF_01e.gif?t=1718390100\" /><br><strong>RESTART</strong> from the beginning of the level with a simple touch until you find the best strategy.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531040/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1718390100","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531040/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1718390100","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531040/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1718390100","capsule_imagev5